name: Hinagiku Katsura (Hayate no Gotoku!)
description:
If you like my works, consider make a donation.

The Princess of Dreams, Angel of Light, Student Council President and Heroine of Justice, Hinagiku Katsura!

The girl who was in top 10 best female characters in late 2000s, couldn't be none other than my favorite female character of all the time.

In V1 I exaggerated the amount of images for training, while it needed very low epochs to be decent, apparently Weight 1 is too much tied with the official anime's style, so you may need to reduce it for different styles, 0.5 or 0.6 works well.

Triggers with hinagiku katsura, and hakuou uniform brings her classic uniform. Supposedly summer uniform brings her white uniform but doesn't work very well, perhaps due to lack of many examples.

V1a is a version less attached to the anime style, you will still need to decrease the Weight to have better results but less than the first V1.

The uniforms are activated with different prompts, hakuoua brings the standard uniform and hakuoub brings the summer uniform. If the results are generic uniforms, try complementary with loafers, school uniform, serafuku, pink skirt; pink serakufu for the normal uniform and white serakufu for the summer uniform.

Tests show that this version works in reverse to the previous one, summer uniform appears more frequent than the normal uniform. If you're having trouble to make the normal uniform appears, consider use the previous version.
